76561197968425750,Recommended,301650,33447562,Posted: 10 July,all,Doc Holliday,"BATTLEZONE IS AWESOME.  It has always been awesome, and this Redux version does a great job of breathing new life into it.  When it comes to these nostalgic remasters and remakes, sometimes I have a hard time determining if a game was truly great, or just seemed great at the time and I was too young to really know the difference.  Rest assured, Battlezone deserves its legendary status.Playing this game reminds you how great gaming can be, and why you've been a gamer all this time.  Most games have obvious inspiration from other titles, and generally follow the same formula within their genre.  Battlezone is a true original, there are very few games even remotely similar.  It's still the best FPS/RTS hybrid, and one of the best RTS games of all time.  The controls are unique, but instantly intuitive and very effective.  I don't understand why nobody has even attempted cloning BZ over the years.All in all I'm very happy this ""redux"" version was made, and very happy I picked it up.  Battlezone would have been a legend in my memory either way, but nobody should miss this chance to relive one of gaming's true gems."
